wikipedia_page.main: Jemma Helen Rose (born 19 January 1992) is an English footballer who played for FA WSL club Arsenal as a central defender. She has represented England, making her debut at senior level in November 2015. Rose was named the FA Women's Young Player of the Year in 2011.
